title: Claude Monet Water Lilies Tea Towel
description:
Tea Towel developed from Claude Monet’s Water Lilies, 1906 from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

This tea towel blend timeless style with modern practicality. Dry your dishes and stay inspired. Consider combining this with the Claude Monet Water Lilies Pot Holder and Apron, for a special gift set.

  • Dimensions: 18 in. x 28 in. 
  • Material: 100% cotton
  • Machine wash cold, line dry.
